{"content":"---\ntitle: \"option <optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc2009\"\n  - \"bc2009\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC2009\"\nms.assetid: 90e5dcf9-37fb-4a97-9f53-4e7c73d6ba9f\n---\n# option \\<optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'\nThe text that follows the option is not a plus sign (+) or a minus sign (-).  \n  \n **Error ID:** BC2009  \n  \n## To correct this error  \n  \n-   Replace the text that follows the option with a plus sign (+) to turn the option on.  \n  \n     — or —  \n  \n-   Replace the text that follows the option with a minus sign (-) to turn the option off.  \n  \n## See also\n\n- [Visual Basic Compiler Options Listed Alphabetically](../../visual-basic/reference/command-line-compiler/compiler-options-listed-alphabetically.md)\n- [Error Types](../../visual-basic/programming-guide/language-features/error-types.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,212],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"option <optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc2009\"\n  - \"bc2009\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC2009\"\nms.assetid: 90e5dcf9-37fb-4a97-9f53-4e7c73d6ba9f","nodes":[{"content":"option <optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'","nodes":[{"pos":[0,54],"content":"option <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;optionname&gt;</ph> can be followed only by '+' or '-'","source":"option <optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'"}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[219,274],"content":"option \\<optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'","linkify":"option \\<optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'","nodes":[{"content":"option <ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>optionname&gt; can be followed only by '+' or '-'","pos":[0,55],"source":"option \\<optionname> can be followed only by '+' or '-'"}]},{"content":"The text that follows the option is not a plus sign (+) or a minus sign (-).","pos":[275,351]},{"pos":[358,378],"content"